{"tid":458090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 警漁灣邨拘毒男","createTime":"2017-11-04T13:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T19:02:44.000Z","uid":37524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c6077a1a2ef03f1356d42e9a6565d064f267ac","tid":458090,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"港島總區特別職務隊人員昨晚10時許進行反毒品行動，在柴灣漁灣邨發現一名33歲姓黃本地男子形迹可疑，遂上前截查，警員其後於黃位於漁順樓的住所檢獲3包共重約17克懷疑冰毒、3個冰壺及一批毒品包裝工具，毒品市值約4950元。黃涉嫌「販毒」及「藏有工具可作吸食毒品用途」兩罪被捕，正被扣留調查，初步調查相信黃有黑幫背景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171104/s00001/1509757711045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171104%2Fs00001%2F1509757711045&d=zC7mDGIpnYL9FmAg5YBBzy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a987d384\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171104%2Fs00001%2F1509757711045&h=8981d52c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171104/s00001/1509757711045</a>"},{"pid":"1d9cf7ebb6f3fdccd5226f39ac4e3b9c554d9f7f","tid":458090,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f3cdbbe79d35a12dc9bcb718c7781a5c5bc1d7","tid":458090,"uid":18948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"$4950<br />\n<br />\n以為係四億毒品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38395f36a4b84f5f6e41cf801db85dbcbcf0bea","tid":458090,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:18:53.000Z","msg":"次次都係拉D 運毒 既卒仔<br />\n<br />\n幾時可以拉背後既大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0c489e10188584d1ea76b54152bc77e7e51f26","tid":458090,